{
  "video_id": "kuT7zWZEwl0",
  "title": "A Parkland teacher's homework for us all | Diane Wolk-Rogers",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 14695.0,
      "text": "I teach history"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14719.0,
      "end_time": 16960.0,
      "text": "at Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18560.0,
      "end_time": 22535.0,
      "text": "On February 14, 2018,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22560.0,
      "end_time": 28880.0,
      "text": "my school experienced one of the worst mass school shootings in American history."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 31200.0,
      "end_time": 34455.0,
      "text": "People want to know what we saw,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 34480.0,
      "end_time": 35680.0,
      "text": "what I felt."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37120.0,
      "end_time": 38800.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t remember everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39840.0,
      "end_time": 43216.0,
      "text": "but I do remember I went into crisis mode,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43240.0,
      "end_time": 44536.0,
      "text": "mother mode."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44560.0,
      "end_time": 45760.0,
      "text": "There was no emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47200.0,
      "end_time": 48896.0,
      "text": "I lined up the kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48920.0,
      "end_time": 51816.0,
      "text": "I held up a sign so they could follow me through the hall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51840.0,
      "end_time": 53160.0,
      "text": "just like a fire drill."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53920.0,
      "end_time": 56800.0,
      "text": "I heard shots from one direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56720.0,
      "end_time": 60000.0,
      "text": "Luckily, we were already moving in the opposite direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61400.0,
      "end_time": 62680.0,
      "text": "We made it outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63600.0,
      "end_time": 65120.0,
      "text": "We made it to safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66200.0,
      "end_time": 67400.0,
      "text": "I called my mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68120.0,
      "end_time": 69536.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m OK.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69560.0,
      "end_time": 71400.0,
      "text": "I called my husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71840.0,
      "end_time": 73456.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m OK.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73480.0,
      "end_time": 77680.0,
      "text": "Then my daughter called, my voice cracked, and I knew I had to pull myself together."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82400.0,
      "end_time": 84960.0,
      "text": "I sat alone in my thoughts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84120.0,
      "end_time": 87160.0,
      "text": "worried about my colleagues and students."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90800.0,
      "end_time": 95560.0,
      "text": "We sat there, only understanding that somehow, Valentine&#39;s Day --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98120.0,
      "end_time": 102256.0,
      "text": "We sat there, only understanding that somehow, Valentine&#39;s Day"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 102280.0,
      "end_time": 105560.0,
      "text": "had ended up with our babies dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 105800.0,
      "end_time": 106960.0,
      "text": "and we didn&#39;t know what to do next."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112680.0,
      "end_time": 114856.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been two months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 114880.0,
      "end_time": 119696.0,
      "text": "and every day I still hear the echoes of the \"pop, pop\" sound of the gunfire."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 119720.0,
      "end_time": 122336.0,
      "text": "I remember the fearful faces of my students"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 122360.0,
      "end_time": 124800.0,
      "text": "when we knew it wasn&#39;t a drill."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 125760.0,
      "end_time": 128880.0,
      "text": "Still, there&#39;s no constant emotion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 129758.99999999999,
      "end_time": 135456.0,
      "text": "except for flashes of pain, grief and anger"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 135480.0,
      "end_time": 137335.0,
      "text": "triggered by the news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137360.0,
      "end_time": 139816.0,
      "text": "or an insensitive comment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139840.0,
      "end_time": 141800.0,
      "text": "or just silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 146440.0,
      "end_time": 151736.0,
      "text": "Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School lost 17 precious lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 151760.0,
      "end_time": 153359.0,
      "text": "on that horrible day."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 157640.0,
      "end_time": 161576.0,
      "text": "After, students asked us, the adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 161600.0,
      "end_time": 163376.0,
      "text": "the hardest question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 163400.0,
      "end_time": 166520.0,
      "text": "How can we stop the senseless violence?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 167680.0,
      "end_time": 171200.0,
      "text": "This was the most difficult question I&#39;ve been asked."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 172560.0,
      "end_time": 176256.0,
      "text": "But it was not the first time I&#39;ve been humbled by a student&#39;s question."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 176280.0,
      "end_time": 179976.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been teaching in the public schools for 33 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 180000.0,
      "end_time": 183416.0,
      "text": "so I know you have to admit what you don&#39;t know"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 183440.0,
      "end_time": 185680.0,
      "text": "before you can share what you do know."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 186320.0,
      "end_time": 191960.0,
      "text": "In fact, there&#39;s a method to being an engaged student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 191120.0,
      "end_time": 193400.0,
      "text": "teacher, citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 193680.0,
      "end_time": 198600.0,
      "text": "First, listen closely to the person asking you a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 200800.0,
      "end_time": 204000.0,
      "text": "Second, admit your vulnerability. Admit what you don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 205720.0,
      "end_time": 208736.0,
      "text": "Third, do your homework."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 208760.0,
      "end_time": 213335.0,
      "text": "Fourth, humbly share your knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 213360.0,
      "end_time": 215536.0,
      "text": "I know all about this process."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 215560.0,
      "end_time": 219656.0,
      "text": "My students ask really thoughtful questions all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 219680.0,
      "end_time": 221296.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re eager to learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 221320.0,
      "end_time": 225790.0,
      "text": "and sometimes they&#39;re eager to prove their smarts."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 225880.0,
      "end_time": 229656.0,
      "text": "And believe me, they know when I have no idea of the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 229680.0,
      "end_time": 232960.0,
      "text": "so in those instances, I say to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 232120.0,
      "end_time": 235880.0,
      "text": "\"That&#39;s a great question. Let me research that and get back to you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 237720.0,
      "end_time": 239816.0,
      "text": "So when my students asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 239840.0,
      "end_time": 242416.0,
      "text": "\"How do we stop this senseless violence?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 242440.0,
      "end_time": 243640.0,
      "text": "I listened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 245160.0,
      "end_time": 246359.0,
      "text": "and then I admitted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 248240.0,
      "end_time": 249440.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t know.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 250560.0,
      "end_time": 254256.0,
      "text": "And like I always do when I don&#39;t know the answer to one of my questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 254280.0,
      "end_time": 256320.0,
      "text": "I began doing my homework."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 258399.0,
      "end_time": 259655.0,
      "text": "And as a history teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 259680.0,
      "end_time": 264120.0,
      "text": "I knew I needed to start with the Second Amendment and the NRA."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 265000.0,
      "end_time": 268896.0,
      "text": "In case it&#39;s been a while since you&#39;ve been sitting in a history class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 268920.0,
      "end_time": 270536.0,
      "text": "here is what the Second Amendment"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 270560.0,
      "end_time": 271760.0,
      "text": "actually says:"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 273360.0,
      "end_time": 275616.0,
      "text": "\"A well regulated Militia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 275640.0,
      "end_time": 279150.0,
      "text": "being necessary to the security of a free State,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 279400.0,
      "end_time": 281896.0,
      "text": "the right of the people to keep and bear arms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 281920.0,
      "end_time": 283480.0,
      "text": "shall not be infringed.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 285000.0,
      "end_time": 288656.0,
      "text": "Meaning, the federal government could not infringe on the rights of citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 288680.0,
      "end_time": 292400.0,
      "text": "to participate in well-regulated militias."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 293400.0,
      "end_time": 298135.0,
      "text": "The Second Amendment was ratified 226 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 298160.0,
      "end_time": 301896.0,
      "text": "It was written in a time before the federal government&#39;s armed forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 301920.0,
      "end_time": 304176.0,
      "text": "were among the most powerful in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 304200.0,
      "end_time": 309000.0,
      "text": "and when state militias were viewed as necessary to protect the states."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 309840.0,
      "end_time": 314176.0,
      "text": "Fast-forward 80 years, to 1871."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 314200.0,
      "end_time": 317536.0,
      "text": "The American Civil War had ended a few years prior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 317560.0,
      "end_time": 319496.0,
      "text": "but a couple of Union officers"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 319520.0,
      "end_time": 323440.0,
      "text": "had witnessed some pretty shoddy marksmanship on the battlefield."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 324800.0,
      "end_time": 328736.0,
      "text": "So in an attempt to prepare their men for any future conflicts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 328760.0,
      "end_time": 331776.0,
      "text": "they founded the National Rifle Association"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 331800.0,
      "end_time": 334400.0,
      "text": "to promote rifle practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 335800.0,
      "end_time": 338416.0,
      "text": "In short, the Second Amendment was written to ensure"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 338440.0,
      "end_time": 341216.0,
      "text": "that our newly formed and fragile country"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 341240.0,
      "end_time": 345216.0,
      "text": "had access to organized state militias."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 345240.0,
      "end_time": 351960.0,
      "text": "And the NRA&#39;s original mission was to ensure future soldiers had good aim."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 354200.0,
      "end_time": 356176.0,
      "text": "Someone could teach an entire course"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 356200.0,
      "end_time": 361216.0,
      "text": "on how the next 150 years influenced the gun regulation conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 361240.0,
      "end_time": 362856.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re having in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 362880.0,
      "end_time": 365520.0,
      "text": "and our interpretation of the Second Amendment."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 366760.0,
      "end_time": 370296.0,
      "text": "Almost every pivotal moment in our nation&#39;s history"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 370320.0,
      "end_time": 371575.0,
      "text": "in one way or another"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 371600.0,
      "end_time": 373416.0,
      "text": "influenced how we as a people"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 373440.0,
      "end_time": 377920.0,
      "text": "manufacture, debate, regulate and feel about guns."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 380800.0,
      "end_time": 381800.0,
      "text": "A lot of change has occurred."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 382800.0,
      "end_time": 386336.0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it wasn&#39;t until 2008"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 386360.0,
      "end_time": 389376.0,
      "text": "that the Supreme Court ruled for the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 389400.0,
      "end_time": 393775.0,
      "text": "the Second Amendment protects an individual right to possess a firearm"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 393800.0,
      "end_time": 396336.0,
      "text": "unconnected with service in a militia"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 396360.0,
      "end_time": 400176.0,
      "text": "and to use that arm for traditionally lawful purposes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 400200.0,
      "end_time": 403135.0,
      "text": "such as self-defense within the home."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 403160.0,
      "end_time": 405000.0,
      "text": "Within the home."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 406800.0,
      "end_time": 410176.0,
      "text": "This change over time is striking to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 410200.0,
      "end_time": 411736.0,
      "text": "because it reminds us"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 411760.0,
      "end_time": 415560.0,
      "text": "that the interpretation of the Second Amendment"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 415800.0,
      "end_time": 417895.0,
      "text": "and cultural attitudes about guns"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 417920.0,
      "end_time": 419640.0,
      "text": "have changed over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 420880.0,
      "end_time": 424560.0,
      "text": "Which gives me hope they could change again."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 425400.0,
      "end_time": 429840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 433480.0,
      "end_time": 436776.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an incredibly complex and dynamic history lesson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 436800.0,
      "end_time": 439560.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not the lesson I&#39;m here to teach today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 439800.0,
      "end_time": 440736.0,
      "text": "because we don&#39;t have time."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 440760.0,
      "end_time": 442336.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not talking about time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 442360.0,
      "end_time": 445696.0,
      "text": "the time that I have here to stand and speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 445720.0,
      "end_time": 450960.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m talking about the fact we don&#39;t have time to lose."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 450120.0,
      "end_time": 452216.0,
      "text": "According to the CDC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 452240.0,
      "end_time": 454496.0,
      "text": "over the last five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 454520.0,
      "end_time": 461176.0,
      "text": "on average, each day 96 people are killed by guns in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 461200.0,
      "end_time": 465159.0,
      "text": "and if we don&#39;t figure out how to answer my students&#39; question soon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 467320.0,
      "end_time": 468960.0,
      "text": "one of us could be next."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 471120.0,
      "end_time": 476256.0,
      "text": "So, if the question is, how do we stop this senseless violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 476280.0,
      "end_time": 478616.0,
      "text": "the best way I can think to answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 478640.0,
      "end_time": 480776.0,
      "text": "is to look at multiple choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 480800.0,
      "end_time": 484000.0,
      "text": "You remember multiple-choice questions in high school, don&#39;t you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 485200.0,
      "end_time": 486479.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 487960.0,
      "end_time": 493176.0,
      "text": "Choice A: this will end when we hold gun manufacturers responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 493200.0,
      "end_time": 495400.0,
      "text": "for the deadliness of their products."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 496200.0,
      "end_time": 500256.0,
      "text": "It might surprise you to learn that we&#39;ve actually thought about this before."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 500280.0,
      "end_time": 503176.0,
      "text": "Between 1998 and 2000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 503200.0,
      "end_time": 507150.0,
      "text": "30 counties and cities sued gun manufacturers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 507400.0,
      "end_time": 509696.0,
      "text": "saying they should make their products safer"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 509720.0,
      "end_time": 513400.0,
      "text": "and do a better job of tracking where their products are sold."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 514840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517696.00000000006,
      "text": "In response, manufacturers argued"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 517720.0,
      "end_time": 521560.0,
      "text": "that they had no direct liability for how their products were used."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 522200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527376.0,
      "text": "They said the stores who sold the guns and the owners who bought them"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 527400.0,
      "end_time": 530120.0,
      "text": "were responsible should anything bad happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 531559.0,
      "end_time": 534960.0,
      "text": "In response to this and many other lawsuits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 534120.0,
      "end_time": 538120.0,
      "text": "the NRA lobbied for the passage of the PLCAA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 539800.0,
      "end_time": 542976.0,
      "text": "the Protection of Lawful Commerce in Arms Act."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 543000.0,
      "end_time": 548336.0,
      "text": "The PLCAA passed with bipartisan support in 2005"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 548360.0,
      "end_time": 550896.0,
      "text": "and entrusts gun manufacturers"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 550920.0,
      "end_time": 553455.0,
      "text": "to design guns safely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 553480.0,
      "end_time": 556880.0,
      "text": "stores to sell those guns responsibly"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 557760.0,
      "end_time": 561640.0,
      "text": "and someone to own and use the gun responsibly."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 563720.0,
      "end_time": 568600.0,
      "text": "And so when 17 students and faculty die at my school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 570200.0,
      "end_time": 574920.0,
      "text": "no one in this chain will assume responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 582400.0,
      "end_time": 584616.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a look at another option,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 584640.0,
      "end_time": 586656.0,
      "text": "Choice B:"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 586680.0,
      "end_time": 589455.0,
      "text": "this will end when we hold ourselves accountable"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 589480.0,
      "end_time": 595216.0,
      "text": "and regulate the estimated 300 million guns available in America."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 595240.0,
      "end_time": 597576.0,
      "text": "Yes, voting is one of the best ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 597600.0,
      "end_time": 600576.0,
      "text": "to take personal responsibility for gun violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 600600.0,
      "end_time": 605536.0,
      "text": "Making sure that our lawmakers are willing to pass commonsense gun reform"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 605560.0,
      "end_time": 610560.0,
      "text": "is one of the most effective ways to get those 300 million guns under control."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 611320.0,
      "end_time": 614880.0,
      "text": "And also, gun owners can take personal initiative."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 615960.0,
      "end_time": 617736.0,
      "text": "If you own a gun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 617760.0,
      "end_time": 618960.0,
      "text": "ask yourself:"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 619920.0,
      "end_time": 621920.0,
      "text": "Do I have an extra gun I don&#39;t need?"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 622760.0,
      "end_time": 625336.0,
      "text": "Could it fall into the wrong hands?"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 625360.0,
      "end_time": 627800.0,
      "text": "Have I attended the latest training?"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 629920.0,
      "end_time": 631656.0,
      "text": "Perhaps as a gun owner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 631680.0,
      "end_time": 632935.0,
      "text": "you should also ask"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 632960.0,
      "end_time": 636160.0,
      "text": "whether you have been taking care of your mental health?"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 636400.0,
      "end_time": 640136.0,
      "text": "When it comes to gun violence, the mental health argument falls flat"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 640160.0,
      "end_time": 643616.0,
      "text": "if we don&#39;t acknowledge our own personal vulnerabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 643640.0,
      "end_time": 644840.0,
      "text": "to mental illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 645840.0,
      "end_time": 649976.0,
      "text": "One in six Americans will struggle with mental illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 650000.0,
      "end_time": 654816.0,
      "text": "If we own a gun, we should be rigorously engaged in the upkeep"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 654840.0,
      "end_time": 657560.0,
      "text": "of our emotional well-being"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 657800.0,
      "end_time": 659160.0,
      "text": "so we don&#39;t pull a trigger"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 659400.0,
      "end_time": 660400.0,
      "text": "in times of illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 661160.0,
      "end_time": 664536.0,
      "text": "Otherwise, we should seriously ask ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 664560.0,
      "end_time": 668400.0,
      "text": "whether we really have the time and attention to own a gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 672160.0,
      "end_time": 675376.0,
      "text": "Perhaps for some of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 675400.0,
      "end_time": 678160.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s time to lay down our arms."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 680880.0,
      "end_time": 682616.0,
      "text": "Then we have Choice C:"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 682640.0,
      "end_time": 685880.0,
      "text": "this will end when we do a better job of taking care of each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 686640.0,
      "end_time": 690536.0,
      "text": "Many social issues affect why people buy and use guns."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 690560.0,
      "end_time": 694950.0,
      "text": "Sixty-two percent of US gun fatalities"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 694120.0,
      "end_time": 698680.0,
      "text": "between 2012 and 2016 were suicides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 699800.0,
      "end_time": 704896.0,
      "text": "yet we call people maniacs and psychos, shaming them."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 704920.0,
      "end_time": 708336.0,
      "text": "We are creating barriers for people that need help."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 708360.0,
      "end_time": 710840.0,
      "text": "Why are we embarrassing each other?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 711720.0,
      "end_time": 713696.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s make it easier, not harder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 713720.0,
      "end_time": 716440.0,
      "text": "for people to access better mental health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 717200.0,
      "end_time": 722960.0,
      "text": "What else? Sexism, racism and poverty affect gun ownership"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 722120.0,
      "end_time": 723880.0,
      "text": "and gun-related fatalities."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 725360.0,
      "end_time": 730296.0,
      "text": "On average, it&#39;s estimated that 50 women were fatally shot each month"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 730320.0,
      "end_time": 733936.0,
      "text": "between 2010 and 2014"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 733960.0,
      "end_time": 736256.0,
      "text": "due to domestic violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 736280.0,
      "end_time": 740336.0,
      "text": "and women are still dying in their homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 740360.0,
      "end_time": 741856.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s empower women"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 741880.0,
      "end_time": 743856.0,
      "text": "and give our young boys a chance to learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 743880.0,
      "end_time": 748400.0,
      "text": "how to work out their conflicts and emotions with words, not weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 749720.0,
      "end_time": 753160.0,
      "text": "And the \"Washington Post\" reported that last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 753400.0,
      "end_time": 756695.0,
      "text": "nearly 1,000 people were fatally wounded"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 756720.0,
      "end_time": 759696.0,
      "text": "by on-duty police officers."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 759720.0,
      "end_time": 763816.0,
      "text": "Talk to Black Lives Matter and the police union about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 763840.0,
      "end_time": 765536.0,
      "text": "We need to tackle this."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 765560.0,
      "end_time": 770280.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 772640.0,
      "end_time": 774136.0,
      "text": "At the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 774160.0,
      "end_time": 776896.0,
      "text": "perhaps people won&#39;t feel the need"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 776920.0,
      "end_time": 779656.0,
      "text": "to buy and use a gun"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 779680.0,
      "end_time": 784496.0,
      "text": "when they all equally feel safe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 784520.0,
      "end_time": 788280.0,
      "text": "healthy, respected and cared for."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 790800.0,
      "end_time": 792216.0,
      "text": "All right, discussion time is over."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 792240.0,
      "end_time": 794816.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s now time to answer the question."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 794840.0,
      "end_time": 797896.0,
      "text": "How do we stop this senseless violence?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 797920.0,
      "end_time": 800400.0,
      "text": "Is it Choice A,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 801800.0,
      "end_time": 803000.0,
      "text": "Choice B,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 804000.0,
      "end_time": 805200.0,
      "text": "Choice C?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 806240.0,
      "end_time": 808736.0,
      "text": "Now, I know what you&#39;re all thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 808760.0,
      "end_time": 810816.0,
      "text": "You remember that multiple-choice questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 810840.0,
      "end_time": 813456.0,
      "text": "almost never end with just three possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 813480.0,
      "end_time": 816680.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s always that fourth, Choice D: all of the above."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 818320.0,
      "end_time": 820440.0,
      "text": "Maybe that&#39;s the answer here."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 822240.0,
      "end_time": 828800.0,
      "text": "Or maybe \"all of the above\" is too easy, and this is not an easy problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 828960.0,
      "end_time": 834336.0,
      "text": "It requires deep analytical thinking by all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 834360.0,
      "end_time": 838776.0,
      "text": "So instead, I&#39;m asking you to do your homework,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 838800.0,
      "end_time": 840976.0,
      "text": "write your own Choice D"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 841000.0,
      "end_time": 843376.0,
      "text": "using supporting detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 843400.0,
      "end_time": 847175.0,
      "text": "And if you&#39;re not sure where to start, look to my students as role models."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 847200.0,
      "end_time": 850456.0,
      "text": "They are armed with incredible communication skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 850480.0,
      "end_time": 854136.0,
      "text": "and a sense of citizenship that I find so inspiring."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 854160.0,
      "end_time": 857839.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 864360.0,
      "end_time": 869776.0,
      "text": "These are public school kids engaged in the issue of gun regulation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 869800.0,
      "end_time": 872520.0,
      "text": "and their endeavor has moved our hearts."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 873800.0,
      "end_time": 875600.0,
      "text": "And they shouldn&#39;t have to do this on their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 876360.0,
      "end_time": 877976.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re asking you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 878000.0,
      "end_time": 879776.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re asking all of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 879800.0,
      "end_time": 881199.0,
      "text": "to get involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 882560.0,
      "end_time": 885000.0,
      "text": "This isn&#39;t a spectator sport."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 885800.0,
      "end_time": 889295.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s the right answer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 889320.0,
      "end_time": 892896.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know. Listen, I&#39;m no gun control expert."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 892920.0,
      "end_time": 894599.0,
      "text": "I teach the humanities."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 895800.0,
      "end_time": 897736.0,
      "text": "To be human is to learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 897760.0,
      "end_time": 901856.0,
      "text": "and to be part of a civilization is to share your knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 901880.0,
      "end_time": 905415.0,
      "text": "This kind of honest, brave and sincere engagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 905440.0,
      "end_time": 907576.0,
      "text": "is what I ask of my students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 907600.0,
      "end_time": 910656.0,
      "text": "what I expect of myself as a teacher"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 910680.0,
      "end_time": 913790.0,
      "text": "and what I demand of you now."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 914320.0,
      "end_time": 917960.0,
      "text": "Every one of you needs to do your homework."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 917120.0,
      "end_time": 918336.0,
      "text": "And then what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 918360.0,
      "end_time": 921736.0,
      "text": "Humbly share your knowledge with each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 921760.0,
      "end_time": 924776.0,
      "text": "Please teach your family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 924800.0,
      "end_time": 926216.0,
      "text": "teach your community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 926240.0,
      "end_time": 930560.0,
      "text": "your city council, your state legislature."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 930800.0,
      "end_time": 932480.0,
      "text": "Teach Congress a lesson."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 933800.0,
      "end_time": 934296.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 934320.0,
      "end_time": 938960.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 938120.0,
      "end_time": 940576.0,
      "text": "Thank you. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 940600.0,
      "end_time": 945720.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}